{"tid":2035801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"明報：警研將記者分類 或只助主流傳媒採訪","createTime":"2020-05-26T06:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T10:07:45.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3d9c7ae2cca2622844c3d5a410dfcead317b2657","tid":2035801,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:20:36.000Z","msg":"【明報文章】警媒關係近日成為政府工作焦點之一。縱使《警察程序手冊》及《警察通例》列明，警隊要求所有警務人員以互諒互讓態度，盡量配合傳媒工作，以及不應妨礙傳媒的攝錄工作，但據悉警方內部認為「從事採訪的」不等同於記者，「身分與權力是兩回事」，警方內部正向前線防暴警員口頭傳達一套識別記者的指引，要求盡量協助主流報章、電子傳媒及部分知名網媒的記者採訪，學生及公民記者則別論。至於最終如何劃線，未有定案，其中一個考慮方案是警方引用政府新聞處的「認可名單」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/觀點/article/20200526/s00012/1590432009303/聞風筆動-警研將記者分類-或只助主流傳媒採訪-文-李先知\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E%2Farticle%2F20200526%2Fs00012%2F1590432009303%2F%E8%81%9E%E9%A2%A8%E7%AD%86%E5%8B%95-%E8%AD%A6%E7%A0%94%E5%B0%87%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%88%86%E9%A1%9E-%E6%88%96%E5%8F%AA%E5%8A%A9%E4%B8%BB%E6%B5%81%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA-%E6%96%87-%E6%9D%8E%E5%85%88%E7%9F%A5&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjYwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=b59d3b7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E%2Farticle%2F20200526%2Fs00012%2F1590432009303%2F%E8%81%9E%E9%A2%A8%E7%AD%86%E5%8B%95-%E8%AD%A6%E7%A0%94%E5%B0%87%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%88%86%E9%A1%9E-%E6%88%96%E5%8F%AA%E5%8A%A9%E4%B8%BB%E6%B5%81%E5%82%B3%E5%AA%92%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA-%E6%96%87-%E6%9D%8E%E5%85%88%E7%9F%A5&h=35bc84bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/觀點/article/20200526/s00012/1590432009303/聞風筆動-警研將記者分類-或只助主流傳媒採訪-文-李先知</a>"},{"pid":"d52c6b29526b1f8996aff89dca67dc72dd98c5fb","tid":2035801,"uid":185045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:21:31.000Z","msg":"歧視小報網媒"},{"pid":"3423f90603c8d958242d3c6b1cf5e35ed6c01b24","tid":2035801,"uid":277992,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T06:25:00.000Z",